sub_title: Interventional Cardiologist at Catharina Hospital Eindhoven
summary:
I'm passionate about helping communities with heart disease by co-operative innovative clinical research for patients of today and tomorrow.

Interventional cardiologist specialised in complex percutaneous coronary interventions and performing clinical research by writing a thesis on the percutaneous treatment of chronic total occlusions.

Subjects of interest.
-	Treatment of complex coronary lesions (CTO, Bifurcations, Left main, In-stent restenosis)
-	Intra-coronary imaging (Optical coherence tomography, Intravascular ultrasound)
